t: Monster Munch - Wikipedia
s: 3 weeks ago - In 1995, Walkers relaunched the Monster Munch brand with a range of four flavours. A new lineup of monsters were introduced and the original shapes of the snack were replaced with a smaller shaped paw using a twin screw extruder instead of the single screw extruders used before.

t: Monster Munch | British Brands: Past & Present Wiki | Fandom
s: March 10, 2025 - Monster Munch are a brand of crisps initially produced in 1977 by Smiths. The brand was first launched by Smiths in 1977, initially under the name 'The Prime Monster', though this was changed a year after launch to 'Monster Munch'. The crisps are formed in the shape of a monster's foot.
